# ğŸ—‚ï¸ Personal Task Manager â€“ Full Stack Web Application

Personal Task Manager is a full-stack task management system that allows users to securely create, manage, and track their daily tasks through an intuitive and user-friendly interface.

Each registered user can:

- Create tasks
- Edit tasks
- Delete tasks
- Mark tasks as completed
- Manage personal task lists securely

All tasks are private and accessible only to the authenticated user.

