## ğŸ“¦ Installation Process (Local Setup)

### Clone the Repository

git clone https://github.com/Deshishiva/Personal-task-management-.git  
cd Personal-task-management-

---

### Backend Setup

cd backend  
npm install  
npx prisma migrate dev  
npm run dev  

---

### Frontend Setup

cd ../frontend  
npm install  
npm run dev  

